text:
The following classes are not included in the distribution but are referred to 
by the TLD /WEB-INF/tlds/TestLib.tld in the jsp-tests.war file:

tags.PropertyEditorTag
tags.TagSupport.thirdPrizeTag


The following class is not included in the distribution but is referred to by 
the TLD /WEB-INF/tlds/tld_uri.tld:

1. tags.TagLibraryValidator.Validator


Because these tags are not included, any test relating to taglibs fail in our 
container.
